  "description": "This individual is an undead human of The Ossuary Hollow, reduced to a light-skinned frame of exposed bone and dried sinew. Gray eyes sit deep in the sockets, fixed beneath a broken brow ridge that gives the face a permanent, judicial severity. Black hair persists only in sparse, stiff patches along the scalp, leaving the crown largely bare. The mouthline is split by old fractures that lock the jaw into a slight, habitual gape.",
